  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_FileOperations_JsonFileHandler'>Class JsonFileHandler    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/FileOperations/JsonFileHandler.cs#L41'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Handles reading and writing JSON files.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public sealed class JsonFileHandler : IJsonFileHandler</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.html'>JsonFileHandler</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Implements</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.IJsonFileHandler.html'>IJsonFileHandler</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Constructors</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.#ctor(Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.IJsonSerializer,Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.IJsonDeserializer)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.#ctor(Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.IJsonSerializer,Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.IJsonDeserializer)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_FileOperations_JsonFileHandler__ctor_Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Serialization_IJsonSerializer_Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_Deserialization_IJsonDeserializer_'>JsonFileHandler(IJsonSerializer, IJsonDeserializer)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/FileOperations/JsonFileHandler.cs#L59'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> class.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public JsonFileHandler(IJsonSerializer jsonSerializer, IJsonDeserializer jsonDeserializer)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>jsonSerializer</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.IJsonSerializer.html'>IJsonSerializer</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The JSON serializer to use.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>jsonDeserializer</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.IJsonDeserializer.html'>IJsonDeserializer</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The JSON deserializer to use.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Exceptions</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.argumentnullexception'>ArgumentNullException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when any parameter is null.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler._jsonDeserializer' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler._jsonDeserializer' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_FileOperations_JsonFileHandler__jsonDeserializer'>_jsonDeserializer    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/FileOperations/JsonFileHandler.cs#L46'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The json deserializer</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private readonly IJsonDeserializer _jsonDeserializer</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Deserialization.IJsonDeserializer.html'>IJsonDeserializer</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler._jsonSerializer' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler._jsonSerializer' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_FileOperations_JsonFileHandler__jsonSerializer'>_jsonSerializer    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/FileOperations/JsonFileHandler.cs#L51'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The json serializer</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private readonly IJsonSerializer _jsonSerializer</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.Serialization.IJsonSerializer.html'>IJsonSerializer</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.DeserializeFromFile``1(System.String,System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.DeserializeFromFile``1(System.String,System.String)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_FileOperations_JsonFileHandler_DeserializeFromFile__1_System_String_System_String_'>DeserializeFromFile&lt;T&gt;(string, string)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/FileOperations/JsonFileHandler.cs#L121'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Deserializes a JSON file into an object.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>[ExcludeFromCodeCoverage]\npublic T DeserializeFromFile&lt;T&gt;(string fileName, string relativePath) where T : IJsonSerializable, IJsonDesSerializable&lt;T&gt;, new()</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>fileName</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The name of the file (without .json extension).</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>relativePath</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The relative path where the file is located.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">An instance of the specified type populated with data from the JSON file.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The target type, which must implement IJsonSerializable and IJsonDesSerializable&lt;T&gt;.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Exceptions</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.io.filenotfoundexception'>FileNotFoundException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when the file does not exist.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.argumentnullexception'>ArgumentNullException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when parameters are null.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.io.ioexception'>IOException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when file operations fail.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.SerializeToFile``1(``0,System.String,System.String)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.SerializeToFile``1(``0,System.String,System.String)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_FileOperations_JsonFileHandler_SerializeToFile__1___0_System_String_System_String_'>SerializeToFile&lt;T&gt;(T, string, string)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/FileOperations/JsonFileHandler.cs#L74'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Serializes an object to a JSON file.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>[ExcludeFromCodeCoverage]\npublic void SerializeToFile&lt;T&gt;(T instance, string fileName, string relativePath) where T : IJsonSerializable</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>instance</code> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The instance to serialize.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>fileName</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The name of the file (without .json extension).</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>relativePath</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The relative path where the file will be saved.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Type Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>T</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The type of the object to serialize, which must implement IJsonSerializable.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Exceptions</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.argumentnullexception'>ArgumentNullException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when parameters are null.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.io.ioexception'>IOException</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.FileOperations.JsonFileHandler.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Thrown when file operations fail.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
